    <item>
      <title>Shant 称波动性最严重时期可能已经过去</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/worst-of-volatility-probably-over-shant-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Jennison Associates 董事总经理 Raj Shant 表示，日本央行周三发出的强烈鸽派信号的重要性不容低估，最糟糕的波动时期“可能已经过去”。他在彭博电视台发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/worst-of-volatility-probably-over-shant-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 08:00:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Legal & General 上半年营业利润符合预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/legal-general-s-first-half-operating-profit-meets-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法律与一般集团有限公司 (Legal &amp; General Group Plc) 公布的营业利润几乎达到预期，尽管今年上半年，由于其固定收益客户调整投资组合，客户从其资产管理部门撤出了 313 亿英镑（400 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/legal-general-s-first-half-operating-profit-meets-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:56:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受美国销售强劲和日元疲软影响，本田利润创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/honda-profit-rises-to-record-high-on-strong-us-sales-weak-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国市场销售强劲克服了中国市场经济放缓的影响，本田汽车公司第一季度的营业利润升至历史最高水平，使这家日本第二大汽车制造商有望再创利润纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/honda-profit-rises-to-record-high-on-strong-us-sales-weak-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉能可因投资者反对而放弃退出煤炭业务的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/glencore-abandons-plan-to-exit-coal-after-shareholders-say-no</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可公司 (Glencore Plc) 放弃了剥离其煤炭部门的计划，而就在九个月前，该公司曾表示将退出利润丰厚但污染严重的业务，但在与反对此举的股东进行讨论后，该公司最终放弃了剥离其煤炭部门的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/glencore-abandons-plan-to-exit-coal-after-shareholders-say-no</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:05:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰银行上调利息收入预期，因利率持续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/abn-amro-profit-beats-as-higher-interest-rates-boost-income</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰银行（ABN Amro Bank NV）上调了贷款收入预期，显示出欧洲高利率继续为银行业提供顺风。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/abn-amro-profit-beats-as-higher-interest-rates-boost-income</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 05:30:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
